Package org.neo4j.internal.index.label

Interface TokenScanStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConsistencyCheckable, Lifecycle
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LabelScanStore, RelationshipTypeScanStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EmptyingRelationshipTypeScanStore, NativeLabelScanStore, NativeRelationshipTypeScanStore, NativeTokenScanStore
    public interface TokenScanStore
extends Lifecycle, ConsistencyCheckable
    Stores token-->entities mappings. It receives updates in the form of condensed token->entity transaction data and can iterate through all entities for any given token.
